<body>
    {%include "components/navbar.html.jinja"%}
    <br>
    <h1 class="text-center special-gothic-expanded-one-regular">FAQ's!</h1>
    <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto wow animate__fadeInUp">
        <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py playwrite-au-sa-uniquifier">What is Hand In Hand?
        </h5>
        <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color">
            <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
            <h5 class="text-color-2">
                Hand in hand is a web apllication in which we aim to create a place where people with disabilities can
                go
                places without worrying about accessibiltiy as this web application allows users to create posts about
                places regarding changes in the accessability options.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto wow animate__fadeInUp">
        <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py playwrite-au-sa-uniquifier">What safety
            precautions are there for kids using this site?</h5>
        <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color">
            <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
            <h5 class="text-color-2">
                For the children, parental permission is needed in order to hire a caretaker,
                ensuring safety for both parties.</h5>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card mt-3 w-75 mx-auto wow animate__fadeInUp">
        <h5 class="card-header h-card-head-color h-card-text-color-py playwrite-au-sa-uniquifier">Are caretakers on this
            site verfied?</h5>
        <div class="card-body h-bg-card-color">
            <h5 class="text-decoration-underline text-color-2">Answer:</h5>
            <h5 class="text-color-2">
                We ensure all of our Caretakers list their training and experience in order for users to decide which
                are best
                suited for them.

        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <hr class="h-card-text-color-sd p-2">

    <footer>
        <h1 class="special-gothic-expanded-one-regular">Additonal Questions?</h1>
        <h2 class="purple-text special-gothic-expanded-one-regular">Contact Us!</h2>
        <br>
        <div class="container text-center">
            <div class="row justify-content-md-center">
                <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
                <div class="col-md-auto">
                    <a href="https://github.com/Brooklyn-STEAM/10040-Integrating-GPS-To-Increase-Accessibility"
                        target="_blank">
                        <img src="/static/icons/github-mark.png" alt="Github Logo" width="50" height="50"
                            class="m-2"></a>
                    </a>
                    <a href="mailto:tordonez@brooklynsteamcenter.org" method="post">
                        <img src="/static/icons/email_icon.png" alt="Email Logo" width="50" height="50" class="m-2"></a>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>

        <form action="mailto:tordonez@brooklynsteamcenter.org" method="post">
            <div class="container text-center">
                <div class="row justify-content-md-center gap-2">
                    <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-auto">
                        <input type="text" id="username" placeholder="Username" class="rounded p-1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-auto">
                        <input type="text" id="question" placeholder="Question" class="rounded p-1">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-auto">
                        <input type="submit" value="Submit" class="btn h-button-color align-middle">
                        <input name="send-to" value="tordonez@brooklynsteamcenter.org" hidden>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col col-lg-2"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
        <br>



    </footer>





